WEBVTT

1
00:13:05.390 --> 00:13:08.130 
你出去的话  会受到别人藐视和嘲笑
Out there they will hate and scorn and jeer.

2
00:13:08.130 --> 00:13:09.660 
我只是一个怪物
Only a monster

3
00:13:09.730 --> 00:13:13.790 
为什么要受别人的诽谤和恐吓
Why invite their calumny and consternation

4
00:13:13.870 --> 00:13:15.700 
待在这里
Stay in here

5
00:13:15.770 --> 00:13:18.500 
-对我忠诚  -我很忠诚
-Be faithful to me -I'm faithful

6
00:13:18.570 --> 00:13:21.480 
-对我感激  -我很感激
-Grateful to me -I'm grateful

7
00:13:21.540 --> 00:13:26.040 
照我说的话去做
Do as I say Obey

8
00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:32.680 
-待在这里  -我会的
-And stay in here -I'll stay in here

9
00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:34.650 
你对我真好  主人
You are good to me, Master.

10
00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:38.250 
-对不起  -我原谅你
-I'm sorry. -You are forgiven.

